sudo raspi-config --> opens the configuration settings menu

sudo shutdown -h now --> turns off rpi

reboot --> reboots rpi

ping -c 3 raspberrypi.local --> checks if rpi is connecnted to your network

ssh pi@raspberrypi.local --> connects with rpi through ssh

tightvncserver --> type into pi terminal to start vnc server

vnc://pi.local:5901 --> go to folder and Command K than copy this into Server Adress and type password
